pg-tools - miscellaneous paragliding scripts
============================================

This is a collection of paragliding-related Perl scripts, including:

  airfilter
    filter out OpenAir airspace above specified flight level

  compeo-tools
    interface with Braeuniger/Flytec GPS-varios

  igctokml
    convert IGC files to KML for Google Maps


Contact
-------

These scripts were written by Chris Webb <chris@arachsys.com> and are
distributed as Free Software under the terms of the MIT license.
